file: MessageEndEvent.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Event\\Lifecycle\\MessageEndEvent"
type: readonly final class
summary: Represents the terminal state of a message lifecycle within the agent core domain. This immutable event captures the conclusion of a message processing sequence for domain event sourcing. It serves as a durable record of message completion for downstream consumers.
